Sharing my go-to haircut request for a fresh, flattering shape:
• Keep the length
• U-shape at the bottom
• Medium layers all around
• Face-framing layers
• First layer starting below the chin
• Soft curtain bangs

This gives volume, movement, and that effortless post-salon feel.
Always carry reference photos and speak up about what you want. Your hair, your rules!

#longhaircut #haircutinspo #hairtrend2025
